<div class="com-share" data-id="7902" data-title="《阿迪达斯亏了好多钱，不光是因为东西丑》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/7902/medium/7902.jpg?1436694697" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/7902.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
